==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unhand
<hw>Un*hand"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>hand</ets>.]</ety> <def>To loose from the hand; to
let go.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Hold off! <qex>unhand</qex> me, gray beard loon!⟦br⟧
Eftsoons his hand dropped he.</q> <rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unhandsome</ent>⟦br⟧
